Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:04.89,中文,,0,0,0,,几周前 一个无形的穹顶从天而降\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A few weeks ago, an invisible dome crashed down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.89,0:00:08.12,中文,,0,0,0,,笼罩着切斯特磨坊镇 把我们和外面的世界隔离\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}on Chester's Mill, cutting us off from the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:10.78,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶为何出现 前方还有什么谜团\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why the dome is here or what mysteries lie ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:11.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我们仍不清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:14.44,中文,,0,0,0,,每天它都在挑战我们的极限\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Every day it tests our limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.47,中文,,0,0,0,,让我们展现人性最美和最丑恶的一面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}bringing out the best and the worst in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.70,中文,,0,0,0,,有人说我们会永远被困在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Some say we'll be stuck here forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:25.74,中文,,0,0,0,,但我们不会放弃寻找到出路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but we will never stop fighting to find a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:28.01,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼 克洛斯 1988年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie Cross, 1988.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.72,中文,,0,0,0,,这是 我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's... me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:31.52,中文,,0,0,0,,这像是一种能量源\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}BIG JIM: It's some kind of energy source.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:32.84,中文,,0,0,0,,放开那个蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That egg needs to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:36.82,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.75,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:39.25,中文,,0,0,0,,到顶点镇的路被切断了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The way to Zenith is blocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:40.88,中文,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是被切断 是完全消失了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, it's more than blocked... it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:42.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我们又能重新成为一家人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And then we can be a family again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:44.58,中文,,0,0,0,,-你这个骗子 -你和那个为了蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You're a liar! - You're working for the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:46.12,中文,,0,0,0,,把我们困住的人是一伙的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}guy who held us captive over the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:47.62,中文,,0,0,0,,-吉姆 -莱尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Jim! - Lyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:48.79,中文,,0,0,0,,既然我们回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}PAULINE: Now that we're back,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.33,中文,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么 我们都需要莱尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}whatever's gonna happen, we need Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.71,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶正在收缩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome's contracting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.01,中文,,0,0,0,,你是说它在缩小\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You mean, it's shrinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:00.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道为什么 但它一会缩小一会又停止\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know why, but it keeps starting and stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:04.03,中文,,0,0,0,,至少它不再旋转和颠倒气候了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}At least the dome stopped spinning and inverting the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.54,中文,,0,0,0,,所以气温才会升高\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's why the temperature's warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:06.75,中文,,0,0,0,,没错 但现在它在缩小\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, but now it's shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.18,中文,,0,0,0,,一开始是地震\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}First, that earthquake struck,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.23,中文,,0,0,0,,然后这里又变得超级冷 现在又在缩小\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then it got super-cold in here, and now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得苍穹会不断进化吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you think the dome could be evolving?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.46,中文,,0,0,0,,最终会变成什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And into what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:14.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我 我也不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I d... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:16.73,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么又开始了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why is it moving again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:18.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我会查明清楚的 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, I will figure it out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.27,中文,,0,0,0,,现在先通知告诉大家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In the meantime, spread the word
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.27,0:01:21.61,中文,,0,0,0,,让大家在镇中心集合\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to get people to the center of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:22.91,中文,,0,0,0,,用对讲机或者到他们家里都行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Use walkies, go to their houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:24.68,中文,,0,0,0,,让大家都过去 马上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just get them there... now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:29.69,中文,,0,0,0,,在这个世界上 任何事物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To everything there is a season,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:34.37,中文,,0,0,0,,都有一套自己的生长时期\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and a time to every purpose under the heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:38.24,中文,,0,0,0,,出生的时期 死亡的时期\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A time to be born, a time to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.47,中文,,0,0,0,,种植的时期\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a time to plant,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:42.34,中文,,0,0,0,,把种植物给\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a time to pluck that which...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:46.75,中文,,0,0,0,,拔掉的时期\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- - is planted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:49.48,中文,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地 又暖和起来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank God it's warming up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.71,中文,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么 我们都会一起克服的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, whatever happens, we'll get through it together,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:52.84,中文,,0,0,0,,只要你想要的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:54.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你听到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:55.75,中文,,0,0,0,,听到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:57.76,中文,,0,0,0,,不可能是蛋的原因 是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can't be the egg, though. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:58.88,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 是其他原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, it's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:04.26,中文,,0,0,0,,莱尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:06.93,中文,,0,0,0,,经历了这么多事情 你应该好好休息一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You should be resting after everything you've been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.37,中文,,0,0,0,,听到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:10.10,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:13.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我想我们马上就要完蛋了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think we're all gonna be resting pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:16.48,中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆告诉你我看见什么了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did Jim tell you about what I saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:19.25,中文,,0,0,0,,在我回来的路上我清楚的看见了地狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A fresh vision of hell on my way back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:20.60,中文,,0,0,0,,他告诉我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:22.03,中文,,0,0,0,,你经历了太多事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:24.40,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你才需要好好休息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Which is all the more reason for you to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:26.68,中文,,0,0,0,,走廊那边有一张小床 跟我来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's a cot down this hallway. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:29.95,中文,,0,0,0,,到哪我都会跟着你的 波林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll... I'll follow you anywhere, Pauline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:48.64,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:49.64,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.47,中文,,0,0,0,,你醒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.30,中文,,0,0,0,,能见到你真是太好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's good to see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.48,中文,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:58.84,中文,,0,0,0,,好多了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.35,中文,,0,0,0,,好像变暖和了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It seems warmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.79,中文,,0,0,0,,寒潮已经过去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Cold snap's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.32,中文,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:11.57,中文,,0,0,0,,詹姆士 我能感觉到有些事情还是不对劲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}James, I can tell something else is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:16.05,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶正在向内收缩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think the dome is closing in around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.20,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会想办法阻止它的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're gonna figure out how to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.91,中文,,0,0,0,,也会让你好起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And we'll find out how to get you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.54,中文,,0,0,0,,其实 我觉得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Actually, I... I think I know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我可能知道答案在哪了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}where I might be able to get some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.42,中文,,0,0,0,,那就去吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我会找人来陪你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll send someone to sit with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.51,中文,,0,0,0,,很好 过来 从这个方向去高中学校\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, come one. Around this way. Get to the high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.54,中文,,0,0,0,,-记住了吗 那里很安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- All right? You'll be safe there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:03:59.50,中文,,0,0,0,,-芭比 你看到了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- JOE : Barbie, you seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.89,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 乔 我知道穹顶怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, Joe, I-I see what's happening with the dome,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我现在正在通知大家离开自己的家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}all right? I'm just helping people out of their homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.42,中文,,0,0,0,,那我们在学校集合\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, let's regroup back at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:06.58,中文,,0,0,0,,等会再和你讲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll talk to you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你应该带着那个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You should take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.54,中文,,0,0,0,,他是你丈夫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He was your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.01,中文,,0,0,0,,那都是过去的事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That was my old life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:33.01,中文,,0,0,0,,能否帮忙把波林的日记递给我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can you, uh, pass me Pauline's journal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.35,中文,,0,0,0,,就在那里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.12,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶让我们失去了太多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome has taken so much from all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:44.30,中文,,0,0,0,,现在又发生了这样的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.73,中文,,0,0,0,,只要我们还活着就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All that matters is that we survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会活下去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And we're going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须竭力活下去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're gonna give it our damndest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:58.44,中文,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:03.03,中文,,0,0,0,,- 天哪 已经接近我们这边了 - 走这边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Oh, my God, it's close. - Okay, let's go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.40,中文,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:08.21,中文,,0,0,0,,听说穹顶正在缩小\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did I hear that the dome is contracting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:10.76,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我亲眼看到的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.95,中文,,0,0,0,,速度有多快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How fast is it moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我还正在计算着 吉姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm still doing the calculations, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.03,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在要做的就是让大家保持镇定 然后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So, just do what you do best, keep people calm, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.57,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.29,中文,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到全新的噩梦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Welcome to our new nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.04,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶开始明显收缩了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's stating the obvious.
