Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:41.38,中文,,0,0,0,,这也就证明那个蛋就是穹顶的能量源\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'd say that proves it's the dome's power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.50,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我是说 我不敢相信穹顶会让我们都没命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, I mean, that the dome would kill us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:47.54,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 难道穹顶告诉过你它是来保护我们的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, because the dome told you it's here to protect us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得我是在胡思乱想吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You think I imagined that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:51.02,中文,,0,0,0,,谁知道 你最好有证据证明\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know. It would be nice to have some proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我很感谢你所做的一切 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, I appreciate what you do, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.07,中文,,0,0,0,,你帮助了大家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've helped all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.59,中文,,0,0,0,,但是根据我们所看到的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But maybe with everything that we've seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.25,中文,,0,0,0,,也许你该承认事情并不是你所想的那么简单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you could admit there's more going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.33,中文,,0,0,0,,-好了 我 -现在没时间争论这些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Okay, I'm d... - BARBIE: Now's not the time to debate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.19,中文,,0,0,0,,知道吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:01.59,中文,,0,0,0,,你说的对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.11,中文,,0,0,0,,打扰了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.09,中文,,0,0,0,,帮大家安顿下来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's help everybody settle in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.23,中文,,0,0,0,,芭比 茱莉亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie, Julia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你们很安全 真是太好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm glad you guys are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我可不这么认为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.39,中文,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.07,中文,,0,0,0,,是亨特 他还有些话要说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hunter, here, has something he would like to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.59,中文,,0,0,0,,对吧 亨特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Isn't that right, Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.72,中文,,0,0,0,,当我跟着你从顶点镇回来的时候 我其实\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, when I came back from Zenith with you, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我在偷偷的替你爸办事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was secretly working for your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:24.93,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.91,中文,,0,0,0,,他勒索我 让我监视你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He blackmailed me into spying on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.44,中文,,0,0,0,,想办法把蛋弄到顶点镇去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to find a way to get the egg to Zenith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:33.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我没这么做  因为大吉姆先把蛋扔了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Which I never got to do, because Big Jim tossed it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:35.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我是站在你这边的 我发誓\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, I am on your side, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.43,中文,,0,0,0,,芭比 是真的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.72,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶外有个军事人员想用蛋做实验\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hunter stopped that military guy outside the dome
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.10,中文,,0,0,0,,亨特阻止了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}from doing experiments on the egg,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.60,中文,,0,0,0,,因为他知道那样会伤害到梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because he knew it was hurting Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.27,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们想不出办法让穹顶停止收缩的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's gonna be a lot more people hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:47.64,中文,,0,0,0,,会有更多的人受到伤害的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if we don't find a way to stop these wall from shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.44,中文,,0,0,0,,芭比 我真的很抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie, I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.31,中文,,0,0,0,,闭上你的嘴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't get to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你们两个去外面帮忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You two go help out.
