Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我说 出去帮忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I said... go help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.05,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.50,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我去看看梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll keep an eye on Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.40,中文,,0,0,0,,-你要干什么 -闭嘴 只管走路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What are you doing? - Shut up and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.33,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.75,中文,,0,0,0,,本\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.57,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.02,中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:52.73,中文,,0,0,0,,一切都完了 诺瑞\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's over, Norrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.80,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不会的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.90,中文,,0,0,0,,我刚刚看见五金店老板的车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I just saw the guy who owned the hardware store
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.16,中文,,0,0,0,,被穹顶给挤扁了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}get his car crushed when the dome smashed into it.
