Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.83,中文,,0,0,0,,过不了多久 我们也都会死的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Before too long, we're all gonna be dead, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.36,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我们不会的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, we're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:09.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一定会找到方法出去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because we're gonna find a way out of here somehow, someway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:11.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不会死在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We are not gonna die in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.93,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道我为什么认为一切都会结束吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know how I know it's all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:15.24,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:17.35,中文,,0,0,0,,因为之前还在抱怨说讨厌这个地方的那个女的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The girl who bitched and moaned about how much she hates
