Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.05,中文,,0,0,0,,- 诺瑞 走吧 - 干嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Norrie, let's go. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我看见芭比带着亨特离开学校了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I saw Barbie leading Hunter away from the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.65,中文,,0,0,0,,芭比看起来很不爽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie did not look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.11,中文,,0,0,0,,-他们要去哪 -不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Where are they going? - I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.50,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我们必须跟着他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that's why we have to follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:34.78,中文,,0,0,0,,不管他们要做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, whatever they're up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.76,中文,,0,0,0,,很明显 芭比不希望我们跟着他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie obviously didn't want us coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:37.65,中文,,0,0,0,,但如果是芭比的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But if it's Barbie, he's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.30,中文,,0,0,0,,他很有可能会想到办法阻止发生的这一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}probably got a plan to stop what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.27,中文,,0,0,0,,你难道不想知道他要干嘛吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't you want to see what he's up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.21,中文,,0,0,0,,但是为什么我们要回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But why do we have to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你以前的画也许会告诉我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because maybe one of your old paintings shows us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.49,中文,,0,0,0,,怎样才能让穹顶停止缩小\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}how we can stop the dome from contracting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我是说 它预言了穹顶的出现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, it showed it coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.51,中文,,0,0,0,,也预言了粉色星星的坠落\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It showed the pink stars falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.51,中文,,0,0,0,,你去看看吧 不过我可能待在这更有用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go, have a look, but I could be of more use here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.00,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么 为了让莱尔好受点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What, comforting Lyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得是这样吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:56.15,中文,,0,0,0,,他简直是疯了 他就是个傻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's out of his gourd. His his was pretty soft to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:58.05,中文,,0,0,0,,你后悔救他了么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you sorry you saved him from drowning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:01.19,中文,,0,0,0,,没有 我是说 你想让他活着 我就这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, I mean, you wanted him here, and, you know, I did it for you.
