Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:10.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你说我不应该接近他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the last place I should be is anywhere near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.09,中文,,0,0,0,,就这样你还是花了六个月才跟他分手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Still took you six months to dump him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.87,中文,,0,0,0,,毕竟还是分手了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I did... eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.15,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 让我们一起解决这个事吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So, let's go solve this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我要见唐 芭芭拉 立刻马上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.81,中文,,0,0,0,,不行 先告诉我情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.29,中文,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 你在这里干嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}James, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:03.06,中文,,0,0,0,,-我来看看梅勒尼 -她好点了么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- It's about Melanie. - Is she better?
