Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.64,中文,,0,0,0,,-等下 谁是梅勒尼 -不关你的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Wa-Wait, who's Melanie? - None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:08.93,中文,,0,0,0,,-我得私下和你谈谈 等等 谁是梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I need to talk to you in pri... - N-N-N-No, who is Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.49,中文,,0,0,0,,你见过她的 梅勒尼 克洛斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've seen her around... Melanie Cross.
