Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.14,中文,,0,0,0,,因为穹顶 它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome, it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.24,中文,,0,0,0,,吉姆 是真的 梅勒尼 克洛斯又活过来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jim, it's true... Melanie Cross is alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.80,中文,,0,0,0,,只是这次 她病的很重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Except this time, she's really sick.
