Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.35,中文,,0,0,0,,-她看起来 很憔悴 -看起来像是病了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- She looked... odd. - Like she was sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.75,中文,,0,0,0,,可能是 我握住她手的时候 她似乎好点儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe, but when I took her hand, she seemed better.
