Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.44,中文,,0,0,0,,-詹姆士 -如果你能画出她健康的样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- James. - If you paint her all healed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.41,中文,,0,0,0,,-她就不会死了 -詹姆士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- then I know she's not gonna die. - James!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:45.20,中文,,0,0,0,,蛋离开镇上之后我就没办法预言了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My visions stopped when the egg left Chester's Mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.35,中文,,0,0,0,,求你试试\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please try!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:47.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不能放弃任何一丝希望\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We have to try everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:51.52,中文,,0,0,0,,詹姆士 我愿为你做任何事请 我是为了你回来这里的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}James, I would do anything for you, I came back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.11,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我的预知能力真的消失了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But my visions are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道我能不能把它找回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know if I can get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:00.22,中文,,0,0,0,,现在梅勒尼快死了 就是因为你搞砸了这一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now Melanie is dying because you screwed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.70,中文,,0,0,0,,你把蛋丢下了悬崖\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and threw that egg over the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.83,中文,,0,0,0,,这些全都是因为你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All of this is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我这么做只是想让你和你妈妈能逃出这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I only did that to try to get you and your mom out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:06.90,中文,,0,0,0,,看看你做的好事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look at the mess you've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.86,中文,,0,0,0,,你找到能帮助她的药了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Have you found anything to help her, yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:18.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你似乎不相信我能找到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You sound doubtful that I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你说你没找到或许我还能好受点 丽贝卡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing would make me happier, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:23.64,中文,,0,0,0,,但是在此期间 你想试试降头术 是么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But in the meantime, you'd like to try what, exactly, a s茅ance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得我是这么想的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that really what you think I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:27.64,中文,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:31.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都想让她和这个镇子变得更好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We both want what's best for her and this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.64,中文,,0,0,0,,但是当你不停的问为什么穹顶会背叛我们的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But while you're busy asking why the dome would betray us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:36.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我却在寻找阻止穹顶杀掉我们的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm asking how do we stop it before it kills us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:39.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你难道没有想过只有找到这两个问题的答案才能救我们么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Have you ever considered it might take both questions to save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.33,中文,,0,0,0,,有可能不是呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Have you ever considered it might not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:43.87,中文,,0,0,0,,-梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- - Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.77,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.24,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.44,中文,,0,0,0,,到底怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:54.32,中文,,0,0,0,,她并没有发烧 我觉得这应该是感染\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She doesn't have a fever, so I doubt it's an infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.74,中文,,0,0,0,,她的身体正在破损\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Her body's falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.96,中文,,0,0,0,,肯定是那个蛋发生了什么事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Something must be happening with the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.54,中文,,0,0,0,,并且伤害到了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And it's killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:20.44,中文,,0,0,0,,可能是很多原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It could be a bunch of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:22.87,中文,,0,0,0,,中毒 免疫机能下降\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}poisoning, autoimmune deficiency...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.81,中文,,0,0,0,,这是她掉头发的原因么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that why her hair is falling out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:25.98,中文,,0,0,0,,可能是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.08,中文,,0,0,0,,还有什么其他症状么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Any other symptoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我只知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All I know is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:31.55,中文,,0,0,0,,自从蛋消失后 她的身体每况愈下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when the egg disappeared, her health went downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.47,中文,,0,0,0,,她的血液怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How's her blood look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.71,中文,,0,0,0,,像她目前一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Same way she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.94,中文,,0,0,0,,她的血红细胞正在急剧减少\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Her red blood cells seem to be disintegrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得给她输血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A transfusion might buy her some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.96,中文,,0,0,0,,是 但是给她输错血型的血 会要了她的命\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, except if we give her the wrong type, it'll kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须要冒这个险\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, that's a risk we have to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我们没有测血型的装备\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We don't have the equipment to type blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:51.79,中文,,0,0,0,,用利马豆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Lima beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.18,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:55.03,中文,,0,0,0,,利马豆中的凝血素\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The lectins in lima beans,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.74,中文,,0,0,0,,它们会在红细胞外壁反应\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}they react to the surface of red blood cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.48,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们将它捣碎 和血混在一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If we mash them up, mix them with the blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就能分辨血型了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we can determine blood type.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.10,中文,,0,0,0,,希望输血对她有用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's just hope she responds to a transfusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:07.30,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么会没用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why wouldn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你以前没有听过这个女孩么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Has anyone told you about this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:11.35,中文,,0,0,0,,她怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:14.55,中文,,0,0,0,,有个奇怪的传言\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's a weird story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:18.54,中文,,0,0,0,,走 安德瑞亚家里应该有利马豆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, I'd bet Andrea has lima beans at her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.17,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:24.54,中文,,0,0,0,,她看起来更糟了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She is worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我们正在尽我们所能救她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're doing everything we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我也是 你知道我妈的日记在哪里么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Me, too. Uh, do you know where my mom's journal is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.54,中文,,0,0,0,,在那个盒子里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's in that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.96,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.73,中文,,0,0,0,,詹姆士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}James?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.49,中文,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信我们竟这么幸运\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't believe we lucked out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:49.25,中文,,0,0,0,,-还是要感谢那些贮藏癖 -是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Thank God for hoarders, right? - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.14,中文,,0,0,0,,你不准备告诉我那个关于梅勒尼的传言么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So, you want to tell me this weird story about Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.92,中文,,0,0,0,,哪个部分 她是我高中女朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Which part? How she was my high school girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:58.14,中文,,0,0,0,,还是她25年前就死了 而现在又活过来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Or how she died 25 years ago, but is now alive again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:01.26,中文,,0,0,0,,-你说什么 -是你问的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Excuse me? - You asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.92,中文,,0,0,0,,山姆 人不可能死而复生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sam, people don't die and come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:06.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我是说 死人可以被药物救活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, they can be medically resuscitated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.66,中文,,0,0,0,,但是不可能在20年之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but not after two decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.16,中文,,0,0,0,,但是 她现在就在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And yet, here she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.03,中文,,0,0,0,,并且她确实是我认识的那个女孩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And that is the girl I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你姐姐假装自己死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your sister faked her own death,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.87,中文,,0,0,0,,-我不知道 或许梅勒尼也是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I-I don't know, maybe Melanie somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.15,中文,,0,0,0,,-丽贝卡 我亲眼见到她死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Rebecca, I saw her die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道死亡是什么样子的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I know death when I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.15,中文,,0,0,0,,你傻笑什么 莱尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why the stupid grin, Lyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:31.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我看你竟然在看你妈妈的画作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I see you have an eye now for your mother's artwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.10,中文,,0,0,0,,真正让我疑惑的是为什么她从来没有预见过你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The real question is why she ever had eyes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.98,中文,,0,0,0,,你妈妈是想要有人来保护她的天赋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your mother saw that she needed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.53,中文,,0,0,0,,而不是怀疑它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}someone to nurture her gifts, not doubt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.34,中文,,0,0,0,,-所以你就是那个人吗 -反正那个人不会是你父亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- And you're that someone? - Well, it wasn't your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:46.21,中文,,0,0,0,,过去九年她给我寄了这些明信片\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She sent me those postcards from the last nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道为什么么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.41,中文,,0,0,0,,因为她相信我能理解这些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because she trusted me to understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.59,中文,,0,0,0,,你想让我对你做同样的事么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You want me to do the same thing for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:54.70,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.20,中文,,0,0,0,,补偿我之前用火钳打了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To make up for hitting you with the fire poker,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.23,中文,,0,0,0,,并且偷了日记\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and for stealing the journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.13,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:06.27,中文,,0,0,0,,能在这里找到什么 或许能帮助梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Find something in here that might help Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:13.29,中文,,0,0,0,,这是你和山姆 妈妈和梅勒尼 对吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's you and Sam, my mom and Melanie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.96,中文,,0,0,0,,是25年前 我们去陨石坑的路上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}On our way to the crater, 25 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.91,中文,,0,0,0,,-也是梅勒尼死的那晚 -这个不会再发生一次了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- That's the night Melanie died. - That's not gonna happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:21.94,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你知道我所知道的 就不会这么说了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If only you knew what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:25.59,中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔 我们会在穹顶里死去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Junior, we're all gonna die inside this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.78,中文,,0,0,0,,别说了 看画吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just focus on the drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:32.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我什么都没找到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I am not seeing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.23,中文,,0,0,0,,你确定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你有画过一条新的隧道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You didn't paint a vision of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:39.01,中文,,0,0,0,,或者洞穴么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of a new tunnel, or a... or a hole in the dome somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:41.35,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我画过 我们现在应该早就找到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If I had, we would have found it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.12,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 我们不会因为我把蛋给丢了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Listen, we are not gonna get crushed in this dome
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.06,中文,,0,0,0,,就被穹顶挤碎的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}'cause I screwed up and threw that egg over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:46.75,中文,,0,0,0,,这里一定会发生什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's got to be something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:48.84,中文,,0,0,0,,你还好么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:51.74,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我很高兴我的血型吻合\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mm-hmm. Yeah, just glad I'm the right blood type.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:54.31,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 如果需要帮助就喊我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right. Give me a shout if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.62,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.32,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我在给你输血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Um, we're transfusing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我会找到你的病因的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm gonna find out why you're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:10.73,中文,,0,0,0,,找不到原因让你有点抓狂 是么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not knowing makes you mad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:12.98,中文,,0,0,0,,有点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:19.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我妈妈给我量温度的时候 都会亲吻我的额头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My mom used to kiss my forehead when she took my temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.94,中文,,0,0,0,,你妈妈也这么做么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did your mom do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我不记得了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.31,中文,,0,0,0,,在我八岁的时候她去世了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She died when I was eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.84,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:34.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我想要一个理由\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wanted a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:38.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我想知道为什么她会从我身边被带走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Someone to tell me why she was taken from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:42.29,中文,,0,0,0,,也许有些问题是没有答案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe some questions have no answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你说话听起来就像茱莉亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You sound like Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.43,中文,,0,0,0,,这是坏事么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that such a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.54,中文,,0,0,0,,比起一无所知 梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's a better thing, Melanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.89,中文,,0,0,0,,知道会更好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:55.95,中文,,0,0,0,,人们总是对这个世界充满好奇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}People have always wondered about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:59.27,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么会有日升日落\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why the sun rises and sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:02.72,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么会有春夏秋冬\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why spring turns to summer and then autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.39,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么爱的人会生病\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why loved ones get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.00,中文,,0,0,0,,怎样才能让他们好起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How to make them better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:14.13,中文,,0,0,0,,知道这些问题的答案不会停止人们的好奇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know, knowing the answers doesn't take away the wonder,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.57,中文,,0,0,0,,只会让这个世界更加奇妙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it actually makes it more amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:21.49,中文,,0,0,0,,那你告诉我 我为什么我快死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Then tell me why I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:25.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我不止是生病这么简单 是么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}'Cause I'm not just sick, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我快死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.33,中文,,0,0,0,,-听着 -重要的是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Listen. - All that matters
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我第一次死的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is, the first time I died,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.26,中文,,0,0,0,,我是一个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.72,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我有你陪着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now I have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.27,中文,,0,0,0,,还有茱莉亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.00,中文,,0,0,0,,还有我妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.81,中文,,0,0,0,,就是为了你们 我回来这趟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was worth coming back
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.46,中文,,0,0,0,,也是值得的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}just for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.78,中文,,0,0,0,,又停止了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's stopping again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.65,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 你的计划生效了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, your plan worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:39.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得把蛋找回来 现在就去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need the egg back... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要那颗蛋 现在就要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望我能帮到你 我不能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.41,中文,,0,0,0,,那么梅勒尼和我都会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:47.45,中文,,0,0,0,,孩子 你知道我愿意做任何事来帮助你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Son, you know I'd do anything to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.43,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我不能把蛋给你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I can't make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:59.37,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 那你的儿子和女儿都将死在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, well then your son and your daughter die in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:08.62,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼几年前就消失了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie disappeared years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.62,中文,,0,0,0,,几年前就已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:13.70,中文,,0,0,0,,不 她现在活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. She is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.17,中文,,0,0,0,,在这里 和我们一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In here. With us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.47,中文,,0,0,0,,还活着 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:23.38,中文,,0,0,0,,不 这不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, that can't be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.06,中文,,0,0,0,,你在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:28.85,中文,,0,0,0,,乔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.05,中文,,0,0,0,,诺瑞 你们两个快点滚出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Norrie! Get your asses out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.97,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我们在跟踪你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How'd you know we were following you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.53,中文,,0,0,0,,当然知道 秘密行动根本不是你们强项\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, because stealth is not your strong suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.90,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 听着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我要说服我爸相信梅勒尼还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need to convince my dad about Melanie, okay?
