Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.51,中文,,0,0,0,,我有更好的 视频博客\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've got something better... A vlog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.27,中文,,0,0,0,,-作为切斯特磨坊镇 -太好了 给他看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}As the newest arrival - Yeah, show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.50,中文,,0,0,0,,的最新到访者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in Chester's Mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.60,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在觉得这儿怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}how do you like it so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.57,中文,,0,0,0,,-每个人都很悲伤 -是啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Everyone's so sad. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.65,中文,,0,0,0,,有什么是我能帮得上的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is there something I can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.12,中文,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.47,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:06.96,中文,,0,0,0,,因为那个蛋把她带回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because that egg brought her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.66,中文,,0,0,0,,如果那个蛋不回到切斯特磨坊镇 她就会死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Without that here in Chester's Mill, she dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我们全都得死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and all of us die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.18,中文,,0,0,0,,又开始了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's starting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要那个蛋 不然我们全都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:24.95,中文,,0,0,0,,芭比 他没明白 告诉他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie, he isn't getting it. Tell him it's more
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.32,中文,,0,0,0,,那个蛋不只是个东西而已 它是有生命的 它认识我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}than just a thing... it's alive somehow. It knows us.
