Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:37.08,中文,,0,0,0,,走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我要把蛋还回去 你们从哪里过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:47.17,中文,,0,0,0,,这样做明智吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is this smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:49.40,中文,,0,0,0,,他可能带他的一整个军队进来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He could bring his whole army through with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:56.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要不然冒这个险 要不然就全都被挤压死在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, we take that risk or we get crushed to death in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.50,中文,,0,0,0,,告诉他通过他房子地窖的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tell him to go through the red door
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.93,中文,,0,0,0,,红门过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of that root cellar at his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你房子地窖红门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.93,中文,,0,0,0,,一切小心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:22.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我们从顶点镇过来是通过那个湖\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The lake's where we came through from Zenith.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.76,中文,,0,0,0,,他们出来的时候需要有人在那儿接应\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Someone should be there when he shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.56,中文,,0,0,0,,看 它停了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, it's stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:30.45,中文,,0,0,0,,-你哪儿也不许去 -我和乔去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You're not going anywhere. - Joe and I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:34.14,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你们俩拿个对讲机再过去湖边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Fine. You guys go get a walkie then head on out to the lake,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.24,中文,,0,0,0,,而且这次一定要藏好 行吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but actually hide this time, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:38.64,中文,,0,0,0,,别被人发现 我爸出现了就用对讲机联系我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You stay out of sight. When my dad shows up, you radio me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.24,中文,,0,0,0,,-去吧 -好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Go. - Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:43.91,中文,,0,0,0,,觉得你爸真能带着蛋来吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Think your dad will really go get that egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:49.94,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶会让我们知道答案的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome'll let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.65,中文,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:02.34,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:06.00,中文,,0,0,0,,-穹顶停止收缩了 -什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- The dome stopped contracting. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:09.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我见了我爸 说服他把蛋带过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I met with my dad and I convinced him to get that egg back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:10.67,中文,,0,0,0,,真的 他一离开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Literally, soon as he left,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:11.98,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶壁就停止收缩了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the walls just stopped shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:14.52,中文,,0,0,0,,也许穹顶也想让蛋回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe the dome must have wanted the egg back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.03,中文,,0,0,0,,当它看到你爸要这样做了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When it saw your dad was gonna make that happen,
