Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:24.73,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:26.04,中文,,0,0,0,,-嗨 -嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Hi. - Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:27.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}how you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:29.48,中文,,0,0,0,,又活蹦烂跳了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:33.05,中文,,0,0,0,,输血有效了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The transfusion worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:34.95,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 输血 还有我们要重新拿到蛋了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, that, and we're also getting that egg back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:36.61,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我才恢复了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's why I'm getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:38.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜只要那个蛋没事了 你就没事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I guess when it's okay, you're okay.
