Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:42.77,中文,,0,0,0,,输血只是一时之计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the transfusion only buys us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:44.74,中文,,0,0,0,,她还是病得很重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's still very sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:46.98,中文,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 她现在是比之前好多了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, whatever it is, she's a hell of a lot better right now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:49.24,中文,,0,0,0,,好吗 我觉得这是最重要的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}than she was. All right? That's all that matters to me.
