Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.06,中文,,0,0,0,,哈喽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:22:58.96,中文,,0,0,0,,有人听得见吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can anyone hear me?
