Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:17.31,中文,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:19.04,中文,,0,0,0,,-枪啊 -是 乔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- It's a gun. - Yes, Joe,
