Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:22.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我要带着它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're taking it with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.41,0:23:24.40,中文,,0,0,0,,不 你要把它放回去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, you're gonna put that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:26.22,中文,,0,0,0,,-别紧张 我看了 它都还没上膛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Relax, I checked. It's not even loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:27.69,中文,,0,0,0,,-是啊 你把它放回抽屉里去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Yeah, and it's not going to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:29.13,中文,,0,0,0,,拿该死的钥匙锁上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because you're gonna put it back in that drawer,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:31.44,中文,,0,0,0,,-才能保证它不会上膛 -诺瑞\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- find the key and lock it the hell up. - Norrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:33.68,中文,,0,0,0,,乔 上一次也是唯一一次你拿着枪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Joe, the one and only time you have ever held a gun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:35.14,中文,,0,0,0,,你差点爆了梅勒尼的头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you almost shot Melanie in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:37.07,中文,,0,0,0,,-对 也就是说 实际上没发生 -我们不可以带着它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Okay, in other words, I didn't. - It's not coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:38.81,中文,,0,0,0,,芭比认为他爸可能很危险\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barbie thinks his dad could be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.99,中文,,0,0,0,,亨特也是 我们要带着它保护自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}dangerous. Hunter does, too. We need it for protection
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:42.75,中文,,0,0,0,,以免他爸想做什么对我们不利\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in case he tries anything when he gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.75,0:23:45.46,中文,,0,0,0,,你想要被保护吗 站我身后啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You want protection? Just get behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:49.33,中文,,0,0,0,,还有 如果唐 芭芭拉带着蛋出现了 他一定会的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Plus, if Don Barbara does show up with the egg, it's gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.33,0:23:51.13,中文,,0,0,0,,因为他想帮助我们 而不是伤害我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because he wants to help us, not hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:53.53,中文,,0,0,0,,-好吧 -我们走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- All right. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:56.03,中文,,0,0,0,,事情不能就这么结束\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not gonna end this way. N-Not after all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:56.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我们已经经历了这么多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we've been through, not after
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:23:58.30,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶甚至都把你带回到我和朱尼尔的身边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the dome brought you back to me and Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.30,0:24:01.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我也希望我能看到些什么来画\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wish I could see something to paint...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:03.61,中文,,0,0,0,,-任何能把我们带离这里的东西 -如果我能帮上忙呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- anything to get us out of here. - What if I can help?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:05.95,中文,,0,0,0,,你不能帮到我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You can't fix me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:08.31,中文,,0,0,0,,就像我正在沉没 苦苦寻找岸边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's like I'm drowning. I'm looking for shore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.31,0:24:09.58,中文,,0,0,0,,却只看到一片漆黑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and all I see is darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:11.82,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你看不到 但是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, you can't see, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.83,0:24:12.99,中文,,0,0,0,,但是你能感觉到什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but can you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.65,0:24:14.98,中文,,0,0,0,,是 我能感觉到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes. I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:20.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我感觉到孤独\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I feel alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.94,0:24:22.04,中文,,0,0,0,,羞愧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:24.01,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.37,0:24:25.98,中文,,0,0,0,,不 因为我自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. Of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.88,0:24:30.48,中文,,0,0,0,,羞愧那么多年前让梅勒尼就那样死去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ashamed for letting Melanie die all those years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.47,0:24:34.37,中文,,0,0,0,,羞愧对你失去信心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ashamed for losing faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.37,0:24:37.01,中文,,0,0,0,,羞愧离开了我的家人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ashamed of leaving my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:38.80,中文,,0,0,0,,不 你没有失去信念\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, you didn't lose faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.43,0:24:42.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我才是失去信念的那个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm the one who lost faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.59,0:24:44.90,中文,,0,0,0,,我没有理解你的天赋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I didn't understand your gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:46.88,中文,,0,0,0,,也 也没理解是穹顶选择了我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}O-O-Or that the dome had chosen us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.59,0:24:49.32,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我理解了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.14,0:24:51.57,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How can you be sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.26,0:24:55.18,中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔被选中把你带回我身边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Junior was chosen to bring you back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.25,0:24:59.39,中文,,0,0,0,,它看到我自愿献祭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome chose to save me before I could hang myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.46,0:25:02.75,中文,,0,0,0,,选泽在我自尽之前解救了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And it healed all those people
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.26,0:25:06.00,中文,,0,0,0,,治愈了所有的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}as soon as it saw I was willing to sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:10.44,中文,,0,0,0,,你被选中了要领导切斯特磨坊镇的人们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You were chosen to lead Chester's Mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.56,0:25:14.25,中文,,0,0,0,,而你被选中给我指明道路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And you were chosen to show me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.51,0:25:24.37,中文,,0,0,0,,看这个 你看到什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look at that. What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.37,0:25:26.18,中文,,0,0,0,,-吉姆 -不 你看到什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Jim... - No, what do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.19,0:25:27.91,中文,,0,0,0,,空白画布\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A blank canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.45,0:25:30.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道我看到什么了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know what I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.00,0:25:33.20,中文,,0,0,0,,全新的开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.82,0:25:48.63,中文,,0,0,0,,那么 你原谅我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.64,0:25:50.29,中文,,0,0,0,,是 我原谅你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.96,0:25:52.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都犯过大错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've both made some pretty big mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.21,0:25:54.82,中文,,0,0,0,,以前你怎么可能会知道那些画\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How could you have known those paintings
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:56.81,中文,,0,0,0,,会变成现实呢 它们都那么疯狂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}would come to life? They were so crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.81,0:25:58.08,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 是挺疯狂的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.71,0:26:15.81,中文,,0,0,0,,不 那是起点镇的方尖石塔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, that's the obelisk in Zenith.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.81,0:26:17.35,中文,,0,0,0,,跟梅勒尼一点关系都没有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That doesn't have anything to do with Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.35,0:26:18.73,中文,,0,0,0,,这里一定有什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's got to be something in here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.73,0:26:20.66,中文,,0,0,0,,表示着梅勒尼的健康\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that shows Melanie healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.66,0:26:22.85,中文,,0,0,0,,给我 让我试着找找\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here, l-let me try and find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.58,0:26:27.48,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我和梅勒尼吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that me and Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.07,0:26:29.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这一张里她看着挺不错的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She looks fine in that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.22,0:26:31.62,中文,,0,0,0,,恩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.76,0:26:33.63,中文,,0,0,0,,不对 在我看起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, the way I see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.63,0:26:36.42,中文,,0,0,0,,这画的是我和你妈妈一起进入天堂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that's your mother and me entering heaven together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.43,0:26:38.37,中文,,0,0,0,,就像我一直希望的那样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just like I always hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.37,0:26:40.00,中文,,0,0,0,,别那样说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't even say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.24,0:26:41.64,中文,,0,0,0,,是你问的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.34,0:26:56.24,中文,,0,0,0,,先生 我知道他是你儿子 但我希望你能三思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sir, I know he's your son, but you need to rethink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.24,0:26:58.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我的直觉已经带我们走到现在这个程度了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My instincts have gotten us all this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.01,0:26:59.23,中文,,0,0,0,,你得相信我 马利克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You need to trust me, Malick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.23,0:27:00.43,中文,,0,0,0,,但你甚至都碰不了它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But you can't even touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.43,0:27:02.83,中文,,0,0,0,,所有靠近它的人都被伤到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's injured anyone that's even gotten near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.93,0:27:09.23,中文,,0,0,0,,乔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Joe,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.23,0:27:10.83,中文,,0,0,0,,有看到我爸的影儿了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}any sign of my dad yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.83,0:27:13.02,中文,,0,0,0,,没有他 没有蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not him, not the egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.02,0:27:14.36,中文,,0,0,0,,什么都没看到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.63,0:27:18.73,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 那就再等会儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right. Well, give it a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.71,0:27:23.05,中文,,0,0,0,,你见到他的时候 他还记得我吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When you saw him, did he remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.36,0:27:26.60,中文,,0,0,0,,记得 一个父亲永远不会忘了自己的女儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, a father doesn't forget his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.90,0:27:30.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我记得他的脸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I remember his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.04,0:27:31.81,中文,,0,0,0,,就是我见过你的那一天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was the day I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.01,0:27:35.67,中文,,0,0,0,,他看起来似乎很伤心 就像他已经知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He seemed sad, like he already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.06,0:27:37.40,中文,,0,0,0,,知道什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He already knew what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.40,0:27:38.67,中文,,0,0,0,,知道如果我们见面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That if we met,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.67,0:27:40.62,中文,,0,0,0,,就不会想说再见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we wouldn't want to say good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.80,0:27:44.45,中文,,0,0,0,,好在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.24,0:27:46.90,中文,,0,0,0,,这一次 我们不需要说再见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This time, we won't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.83,0:27:51.74,中文,,0,0,0,,芭芭拉先生 不要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mr. Barbara, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.85,0:28:07.01,中文,,0,0,0,,是时候做我该做的事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Time to do what I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.61,0:28:13.25,中文,,0,0,0,,-怎么回事 -先生 你需要留在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What the hell? - Sir, that needs to remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.26,0:28:16.43,中文,,0,0,0,,-让他们退下 马利克 -我听命于人 就像你一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Tell 'em to back off, Malick. - I take orders, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.09,0:28:24.39,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.39,0:28:25.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.77,0:28:27.67,中文,,0,0,0,,冷静下来 山姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stay calm. Sam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.67,0:28:30.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为他答应了要帮我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I thought he promised to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.75,0:28:34.48,中文,,0,0,0,,没事的 坚持住 梅勒尼 山姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, hang in there, Melanie. Sam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.48,0:28:36.94,中文,,0,0,0,,-怎么了 -她不能好好呼吸了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What happened? - She was having trouble breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.94,0:28:38.57,中文,,0,0,0,,她刚刚晕过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She just passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.71,0:28:41.13,中文,,0,0,0,,坚持住\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.42,0:29:02.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道我们搞砸了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know we've screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.70,0:29:05.90,中文,,0,0,0,,一次又一次\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.73,0:29:09.40,中文,,0,0,0,,但是就算是发生了这一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But even with everything that's happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.40,0:29:12.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我仍然选择相信你是在保护我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I still choose to believe you're trying to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.75,0:29:15.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为当你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think that when you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.68,0:29:18.53,中文,,0,0,0,,停止移动时 是在用你自己的方式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}stopped moving, that was your way of giving all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.53,0:29:21.25,中文,,0,0,0,,给我们另一次机会 因此我要再求你一件事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}another chance, so I need to ask you for one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.93,0:29:24.67,中文,,0,0,0,,求你救救梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please help Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.40,0:29:29.60,中文,,0,0,0,,她应该活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She deserves to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.02,0:29:34.22,中文,,0,0,0,,这里的每一个人都该活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everyone in here does.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.58,0:29:42.84,中文,,0,0,0,,你说过 我是被选中的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You said that I was chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.50,0:29:46.14,中文,,0,0,0,,那么 如果我是 那一定是为了完成什么事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, if I was, then that has to be for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.14,0:29:48.35,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 如果有人必须死 那就让我死好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So if someone has to die, then let it be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.15,0:29:51.32,中文,,0,0,0,,求求你 别再带走他们中的任何一人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just please, don't take any more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.88,0:30:33.22,中文,,0,0,0,,-打扰一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.94,0:30:38.16,中文,,0,0,0,,-怎么了 -开始起作用了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- How's it going? - It started working.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.16,0:30:39.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我的预知能力回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A vision came through.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.31,0:30:42.75,中文,,0,0,0,,-你画了两幅画吗 -没有 只有一副\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You painted two? - No, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.34,0:30:46.46,中文,,0,0,0,,画中有显示我该怎么拯救整个镇吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Does it show me how to save the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.46,0:30:48.46,中文,,0,0,0,,不 会比朱尼尔想要的多更多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, it's more what Junior wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.12,0:30:52.92,中文,,0,0,0,,-你得继续画 -我不行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You need to keep painting then. - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.51,0:30:56.22,中文,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, what's it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.22,0:30:59.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我不确定 但我想它告诉我们该怎么就梅勒尼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not sure, but I think it tells us how to save Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.78,0:31:03.38,中文,,0,0,0,,那八个人能治好她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The eight hands are to heal her?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.39,0:31:06.18,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我知道为什么我要山姆和莱尔跟我一起回来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now I know why I wanted Sam and Lyle to come back with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.19,0:31:08.94,中文,,0,0,0,,八个人 四个过去的人 四个新人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The eight hands... four old, four new...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.94,0:31:11.71,中文,,0,0,0,,共同努力能把她治好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}working together to make her well again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.71,0:31:14.64,中文,,0,0,0,,是 但是安琪已经死了 现在该只有七个人 谁是第八个人呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, but Angie's dead, so there's only seven. Who's the eight?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.64,0:31:16.82,中文,,0,0,0,,-我不知道 -不要紧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I don't know. - Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.82,0:31:18.23,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶知道的就了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.23,0:31:21.00,中文,,0,0,0,,还有 只要是你画出来的 就会成真的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Besides, if you painted it, it must be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.42,0:31:24.02,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们该从哪里找起 -学校\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Where do we start? - The school.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.02,0:31:25.45,中文,,0,0,0,,好 走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.05,0:31:42.32,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我第一次见到你呆坐着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's the first time I've seen you sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.32,0:31:43.72,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼怎么样了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How's Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.72,0:31:46.09,中文,,0,0,0,,她回复到原来的样子了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's back to the way she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.99,0:31:49.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我不明白 山姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I just don't get it, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.64,0:31:51.54,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么输血起不来作用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why the transfusion didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.54,0:31:54.14,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么她有好转 为什么好转之后又病了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why she got better, why she got sick again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.85,0:31:56.72,中文,,0,0,0,,大部分原因在于她本身吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Most of all, who she even is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.72,0:31:59.29,中文,,0,0,0,,她时隔多年才回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Her coming back after all these years contradicts
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.29,0:32:01.93,中文,,0,0,0,,违反了物理学生物学的定律\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}every law of physics, biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.93,0:32:05.26,中文,,0,0,0,,而那是 那是我一直以来都相信的存在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's-that's everything that I have ever believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.19,0:32:08.62,中文,,0,0,0,,科学无法解释世间一切事物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Science doesn't have every answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.20,0:32:12.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是没有办法像你和茱莉亚那样屈服\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, I just can't give up like you and Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.74,0:32:15.14,中文,,0,0,0,,那不是屈服 而是释然\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not giving up. It's letting go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.14,0:32:16.65,中文,,0,0,0,,屈服和释然是不同的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.48,0:32:18.36,中文,,0,0,0,,有什么不同\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Which is?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.84,0:32:20.02,中文,,0,0,0,,知道并且接受世界上有些事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Knowing there are things
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.03,0:32:22.20,中文,,0,0,0,,是你所不知道的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you don't know and still being okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.40,0:32:25.63,中文,,0,0,0,,走吧 你和我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, what do you say
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.64,0:32:27.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一起去面对这个不确定事件怎么样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you and I go face this uncertainty together?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.34,0:32:33.89,中文,,0,0,0,,也只能这样了 对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Guess that's an answer I'll have to accept, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.89,0:32:35.07,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼在哪里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where's Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.08,0:32:36.90,中文,,0,0,0,,问这个干什么 -我花了一幅预知画\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why? - I painted a vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.90,0:32:38.57,中文,,0,0,0,,可能显示了我们要怎么救她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It may show us how to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.58,0:32:39.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你相信这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And you're in on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.65,0:32:41.18,中文,,0,0,0,,重要的是你要相信我的妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All that matters is you believe my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.44,0:32:43.16,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们能救梅勒尼 那我们就能救这个镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If we can save Melanie, we can save this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.16,0:32:44.32,中文,,0,0,0,,那么 我们最好动作快点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, we better hurry. The
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.32,0:32:46.50,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶又在收缩了 这一次收缩的速度比之前都快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}dome is closing in again, this time, even faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.82,0:32:49.39,中文,,0,0,0,,他没有出现在湖边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So he didn't show up at the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.39,0:32:51.43,中文,,0,0,0,,没有 但是波林觉得她找了治疗梅勒尼的方法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, but Pauline thinks there's a way to heal Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.44,0:32:52.89,中文,,0,0,0,,不用唐把蛋带来吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Without Don bringing the egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.90,0:32:55.45,中文,,0,0,0,,波林要我们一起 老成员和新成员一起去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pauline wants us all together... the old and new hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.92,0:32:57.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我能去吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.19,0:32:58.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你都大老远跑来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.14,0:33:01.97,中文,,0,0,0,,-你准备好了吗 -是的 随时可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You ready to go? - Yeah, just tell us when.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.97,0:33:03.54,中文,,0,0,0,,-你也一起去吗 -嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You're coming, too? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.54,0:33:05.86,中文,,0,0,0,,对这个不科学的世界里所有事情的不确定激起你的兴趣了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wasn't sure anything this unscientific would interest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.87,0:33:08.93,中文,,0,0,0,,如果有方法能够治疗梅勒尼 那我要去见识见识\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, if this is a way to heal Melanie, I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.87,0:33:12.05,中文,,0,0,0,,也许我们都是对的 茱莉亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe we can both be right, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.67,0:33:16.10,中文,,0,0,0,,是真的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.53,0:33:19.20,中文,,0,0,0,,穹顶真的收缩得更快了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dome's contracting faster now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.20,0:33:21.23,中文,,0,0,0,,这也正是我们需要加快动作的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's exactly why we need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.24,0:33:23.72,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我们爸爸没有做到他答应我们的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So, our dad didn't do what he promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.10,0:33:29.43,中文,,0,0,0,,重要的是我答应了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All that matters is what I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.96,0:33:31.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会让你好起来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're gonna make you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.55,0:33:36.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你确定这能帮到她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You sure this'll help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.75,0:33:39.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我只能确定我们必须试一试\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm only sure that we have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.26,0:33:43.57,中文,,0,0,0,,不管今天会发生什么事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No matter what happens today,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.86,0:33:45.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你 詹姆士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I love you, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.04,0:33:48.53,中文,,0,0,0,,永远别忘记\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Never forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.91,0:33:50.27,中文,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.28,0:33:52.08,中文,,0,0,0,,多年前 我抛下了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Years ago, I left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.08,0:33:53.93,中文,,0,0,0,,那是个错误\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.66,0:33:55.89,中文,,0,0,0,,再也不会发生那样的事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not gonna happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.89,0:33:58.43,中文,,0,0,0,,我原谅你 妈妈 但为什么你现在要说这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I forgive you, Mom, but why are you saying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.32,0:34:04.52,中文,,0,0,0,,-没事吧 -我们很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Everything okay here? - We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.64,0:34:07.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我们准备开始吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's get ready to head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.22,0:34:12.06,中文,,0,0,0,,还有 詹姆士 试着原谅他吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And, James, please try to forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.76,0:34:27.72,中文,,0,0,0,,他在这里做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell's he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.73,0:34:29.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道的 他是最初的四个人之一\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know he's one of the original four.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.96,0:34:32.08,中文,,0,0,0,,今天天气真好 很适合做好事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's a great day to do something wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.08,0:34:34.12,中文,,0,0,0,,离我的家人远点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stay away from my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.21,0:34:43.86,中文,,0,0,0,,我回来切尔斯特磨坊镇的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When I came back to Chester's Mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.86,0:34:45.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我梦见梅勒尼就在中央\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I had a dream of seeing Melanie in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.50,0:34:46.70,中文,,0,0,0,,把她放在那里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Put her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.01,0:34:54.56,中文,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.94,0:34:58.17,中文,,0,0,0,,把她放着这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Put her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.52,0:35:04.68,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.96,0:35:06.84,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 你会没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, you're gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.16,0:35:14.21,中文,,0,0,0,,然后呢 现在要做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.21,0:35:15.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是很确定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not exactly sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.55,0:35:16.98,中文,,0,0,0,,那幅画太抽象了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The painting was more symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.98,0:35:18.02,中文,,0,0,0,,-她快不能呼吸了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Well, she's barely breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.03,0:35:19.37,中文,,0,0,0,,-芭比 别吵她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- BIG JIM: Barbie, let her do her thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.85,0:35:23.38,中文,,0,0,0,,所有人围着她 跪下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All hands surround her. Everyone kneel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.38,0:35:25.89,中文,,0,0,0,,朱尼尔 你抓着她的手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Junior, you grab her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.89,0:35:28.28,中文,,0,0,0,,其他人 准备把一只手放在她身上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everyone else, get ready to lay a hand on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.16,0:35:31.84,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 现在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.31,0:35:45.20,中文,,0,0,0,,什么事都没有发生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.21,0:35:46.59,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们 我们是不是做错了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Are we... are we doing something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.59,0:35:47.46,中文,,0,0,0,,-吉姆 也许你是对的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Jim, maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.46,0:35:49.27,中文,,0,0,0,,没有安琪 我们人员不齐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We don't have enough hands without Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.27,0:35:51.92,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们必须治好她 -我很抱歉 我正在努力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- We have to heal her. - I'm sorry. I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.84,0:35:54.35,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 她怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, what's happening to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.35,0:35:56.18,中文,,0,0,0,,-她在接收我们的能量 -八个人没有全部到齐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- She's seizing. - PAULINE: We can't do it, not
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.18,0:35:58.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我们没有办法救她 我们只有七个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}without all the eight hands. We only have seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.07,0:35:59.99,中文,,0,0,0,,等等 我们有八个人的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wait. We do have eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.00,0:36:01.53,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒妮算两个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie counts as two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.53,0:36:04.20,中文,,0,0,0,,过去的她 还有现在的她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The girl she was in the past, and the girl she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.20,0:36:05.52,中文,,0,0,0,,代替安琪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Replacing Angie?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.52,0:36:06.83,中文,,0,0,0,,但是她没有办法一次充当两个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She can't be two people at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.83,0:36:07.73,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不是两个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, not two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.73,0:36:10.46,中文,,0,0,0,,是不同时间里的同一个人 在过去和在现在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The same person in two different times, past and present.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.62,0:36:13.20,中文,,0,0,0,,按量子力学理论 一个物体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Quantum physics says an object...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.20,0:36:14.55,中文,,0,0,0,,一个物体能在同一时间出现在两个不同的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}An object can be in two places at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.55,0:36:18.70,中文,,0,0,0,,就是这样 所以 如果梅勒尼是过去和现在的桥梁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Exactly. So if Melanie is the bridge between past and present,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.70,0:36:21.05,中文,,0,0,0,,-那么第七和第八个人就是 有人牵着她的另一只手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- the seventh and eighth hand... - Someone take her other hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.05,0:36:23.14,中文,,0,0,0,,詹姆士 你是现在的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}James, you're the hand from the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.47,0:36:26.14,中文,,0,0,0,,山姆 你是25年前和她交往的人 你来牵她的手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sam, you dated her 25 years ago. You do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.27,0:36:28.27,中文,,0,0,0,,其他人再次把你们的一只手放在她身上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everyone else lay a hand on her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.21,0:36:30.58,中文,,0,0,0,,有作用了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.58,0:36:32.50,中文,,0,0,0,,她停止接收能量了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Her seizures stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.50,0:36:34.50,中文,,0,0,0,,不要放手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.12,0:36:40.42,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.03,0:36:44.19,中文,,0,0,0,,-怎么回事 -冷静点 莱尔 没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What the hell is happening? - Steady, Lyle. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.20,0:36:45.10,中文,,0,0,0,,没事的 莱尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's okay, Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.40,0:36:47.59,中文,,0,0,0,,她要醒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's waking!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.91,0:36:50.77,中文,,0,0,0,,梅勒尼 你没事吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Melanie, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.32,0:36:55.47,中文,,0,0,0,,她看起比我好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She looks better than okay to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.87,0:36:58.20,中文,,0,0,0,,波林\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pauline.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.35,0:37:01.41,中文,,0,0,0,,这太美好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's so beautiful.
